@startuml
title Place Order Sequence

actor User
participant Frontend
participant Backend
database Database
participant PaymentProvider

User -> Frontend: Click checkout
Frontend -> Backend: POST /orders
Backend -> Database: Validate cart and product stock
Database --> Backend: Cart and stock details
Backend -> PaymentProvider: Authorize payment
PaymentProvider --> Backend: Payment approved
Backend -> Database: Create order and update stock
Database --> Backend: Order saved
Backend --> Frontend: Order confirmation
Frontend --> User: Show success message

@enduml
